    "description": "Lambert, Devan, and Jaskya are Ley Sensitives, gifted people with supernatural abilities. <br>But what is the story behind these powers? <br><br>Join 8 different characters on a journey where they learn more about themselves, <br>their talents, and how they are part of a larger plan that will decide the fate of the <br>world of Orphania and beyond.<br><br><strong>Leyline Chronicles is a classic JRPG and a tribute to the retro RPGs of the 90s and offers:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>A vast world filled with diverse regions, monsters, bustling cities, and small side stories that all weave into the epic main storyline.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/e14a9111c69bd3673ff4ae98b66c176c.poster.avif?t=1767379603\" width=600 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/e14a9111c69bd3673ff4ae98b66c176c.webm?t=1767379603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/e14a9111c69bd3673ff4ae98b66c176c.mp4?t=1767379603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Over eight unique characters, each with side stories that reveal and explore their backgrounds and motivations.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/78ec1b70f83e147976ffe2192ca77d8d.avif?t=1767379603\" width=524 height=232 /></span><br><br></li><li><strong>A turn-based combo combat system with voice acting that rewards strategic, forward-thinking gameplay.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/871e73efa0202aca93d0db5867388659.poster.avif?t=1767379603\" width=600 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/871e73efa0202aca93d0db5867388659.webm?t=1767379603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/871e73efa0202aca93d0db5867388659.mp4?t=1767379603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Trouble Quad! A thrilling card mini-game inspired by Triple Triad. Collect powerful cards and battle your way through the secret tournament against the world’s top challengers.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/dcf482e6fd64d5976a1121b8ee126edb.poster.avif?t=1767379603\" width=600 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/dcf482e6fd64d5976a1121b8ee126edb.webm?t=1767379603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147140/extras/dcf482e6fd64d5976a1121b8ee126edb.mp4?t=1767379603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>A streamlined crafting system that lets you upgrade weapons and armor, unlocking new skills and combos for your party.</strong></li></ul>",
